import { Modal, Heading, Paragraph } from '@contentful/f36-components';
import React from 'react'

function CreateFeatureFlagModal(props) {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <Modal onClose={() => props.onModalClose()} isShown={props.isShown}>
         {() => (
         <>
            <Modal.Header
               title="Create Feature Flag"
            />
            <Modal.Content>
               <Heading>
                  First entry published! It can now be fetched via the APIs
               </Heading>
               <Paragraph>
                  To discover more about how to consume content from the APIs, go
                  to Space Home.
               </Paragraph>
            </Modal.Content>
         </>
         )}
      </Modal>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default CreateFeatureFlagModal;
